(enableSFBOpt, DCacheMiss).explanation: Store-to-load forwarding optimization can reduce data cache misses by allowing direct forwarding of store data to loads, bypassing cache access;

(enableSFBOpt, nDCacheMSHRs).explanation: The number of data cache MSHRs is a static hardware configuration parameter that is not affected by enabling store-to-load forwarding optimization;

(enableSFBOpt, nL2TLBEntries).explanation: The number of L2 TLB entries is a fixed hardware configuration that is independent of store-to-load forwarding optimization settings;
